esponsible for all possible consequences&rsquo;,&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n好霸氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不愧為十里山路不換肩，每日游水游1000米既男人<br />\n碎愛雜總<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a20fa3573071ae8d539bfd0a0825ce81aacc2a65","tid":1141692,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee62bcb3e8d8b9fb331de91ae5923c6249b793ea","tid":1141692,"uid":81113,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T15:59:31.000Z","msg":"連登仔 ? don&rsquo;t know English <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T16:39:24.000Z","msg":"3個負皮，但連埋我先得3個回覆，你地話，我有冇講錯先？"},{"pid":"6b59a2e0c92f1b6a83924d6d9667d7f98edc0fe7","tid":1141692,"uid":1989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T16:42:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://money.udn.com/money/story/10511/3796349\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmoney.udn.com%2Fmoney%2Fstory%2F10511%2F3796349&d=9OMcXw0STyGFZrzowU4xHudFAmKeyJhstBKVrdqrVyA%3D&h=d59cd563\" target=\"_blank\">https://money.udn.com/money/story/10511/3796349</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5e859dba7a542f86c13b1d4ac2a8236d31f7b92","tid":1141692,"uid":1989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b59a2e0c92f1b6a83924d6d9667d7f98edc0fe7","tid":1141692,"uid":1989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T16:42:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://money.udn.com/money/story/10511/3796349\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmoney.udn.com%2Fmoney%2Fstory%2F10511%2F3796349&d=9OMcXw0STyGFZrzowU4xHudFAmKeyJhstBKVrdqrVyA%3D&h=d59cd563\" target=\"_blank\">https://money.udn.com/money/story/10511/3796349</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T16:50:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">中美談判若搞砸 傳習近平自承負完全責任</span><br />\n2019-05-06 15:36中央社 台北6日電<br />\n\t\t<br />\n美國總統川普突然威脅對中國商品加徵關稅，引發中美貿易談判生變的猜測。香港南華早報報導，川普對中方讓步不夠感到不耐煩，而拒絕更多讓步的中國國家主席習近平表示自己會負完全責任。<br />\n川普當地時間5日推文說，由於中國試圖重新協商、談判牛步，將自10日起對2000億美元的中國商品加徵懲罰性關稅，稅率從10%上調至25%。他還揚言，將在短期內對額外的3250億美元中國商品徵收25%的關稅。<br />\n<br />\n川普放話前，中方談判負責人、國務院副總理劉鶴原訂6日率團赴美，展開新一輪貿易談判。對此，南華早報今天報導，中方在川普放話後已做了新的安排。<br />\n報導參與最新簡報的消息人士表示，方案之一是完全取消劉鶴率團赴美；另一個可能性是劉鶴延後訪美日期，改為本週四（9日）出訪華府，但只停留一天，隔天隨即返國。<br />\n<br />\n報導說，川普威脅加徵懲罰性關稅與中方讓步不夠有關。對此，另一名知曉內情的消息人士暗示，此事與習近平有關。<br />\n據透露，談判團隊呈交習近平的協議提案中包含了更多讓步的承諾，但是習近平否決了談判團隊的建議。<br />\n<br />\n消息人士說，習近平告訴談判團隊：「我會對所有可能的結果負責。」<br />\n<br />\n報導表示，中方談判團隊最後提交給華府的提案變得較為強硬，但不確定中方是否在上週舉行的最近一次磋商之後，將修訂的提案交給美方。<br />\n<br />\n對於川普這次的表態，中國大陸學者認為，這是美方希望中國多讓步的策略，想再賺得便宜；但若美方執意施行，貿易談判將再度中斷。"},{"pid":"a528120ad021b68b626f77fede90a3413acca603","tid":1141692,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T16:50:55.000Z","msg":"改革開放幹部不惜折磨可憐的江澤民，一定要拖他出來遊街，就是知道如果2023年不能逼退習近平，大家都要家破人亡。習近平已經無我了，就是說下定決定拖著所有中國人一起死。當然，這對諸夏愛國者或八個大大有利⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/liuzhongjing/status/1125368231387172865?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fliuzhongjing%2Fstatus%2F1125368231387172865%3Fs%3D21&d=9OMcXw0STyGFZrzowU4xHudFAmKeyJhstBKVrdqrVyA%3D&h=8cac3eb1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fliuzhongjing%2Fstatus%2F1125368231387172865%3Fs%3D21&h=780e31c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/liuzhongjing/status/1125368231387172865?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n睇得明呢條tweet既人IQ有100<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6e1cacdbca2ce8814a66998e13bca54b4b542ad","tid":1141692,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T16:52:53.000Z","msg":"所謂既負全責：對不始，禾錯喇"},{"pid":"4b12c71d24728e0746ec459218e3ccf5